The energy nife went into Sinnertwins head, and it spouted some oil out of
it. "Grrrrrrrrr" this one head was enraged, the other that had bit her held
on hard, and the one that was just stabbed began to breath fire on Condor,
emiting a huge hot stream of searing flame onto Condor. "We cook Autobot
before we eat" he hissed between flames. He also put one of his paws on
Condor, and began to slash up and down with his razor sharp talons. "We rip
Autobot too".
